{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_37","type":"agent_message","text":"CI feeds `run-consecutive-tests` with coordinates derived from changed index entries, not from existing metadata directories. That means the coordinate resolver has to accept “index entry + test project” artifacts too; otherwise the job dies before it reaches the actual library under test. I’m checking the existing test-only metadata support and then I’ll patch the resolver conservatively."}}
